title: G5-P2 LF Scrim on EUW
body:
Hi, 
we are a pretty new Team ranging from Gold 5 to Platinum 2 looking for a team around the same Elo to Scrim with withing the next 5h (until 01:00 am cet).
If you are 5 people and interested in playing against us either answer under this post or add "LOW IQ TEAM" in League.
